import Modal from "../UI/Modal";

export default function TollForm() {
  return (
    <Modal>
      <form>
        <label>Toll Name*</label>
        <input type="text"/>

        <label>Vehicle Fare details*</label>
        <label>Car/Jeep/Van: 
            <input type="number" />
        </label>
        <label>LCV: 
            <input type="number" />
        </label>
        <label>Truck/Bus: 
            <input type="number" />
        </label>
        <label>Heavy vehicle: 
            <input type="number" />
        </label>
      </form>
    </Modal>
  );
}
